layphoto-shrink_800_800/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0/1665300965256?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=wG2eNnj-GSa-3DwMLNJjdGEuNwXokXn_LyZYiK8dLfY", "publicIdentifier": "leokauranen", "recommendations/0/context": "Leo managed Valeria directly", "recommendations/0/date": "April 11, 2015", "recommendations/0/description": "I initially hired Valeria through the Direct Marketing Education Foundation, a highly coveted program for graduating college seniors.  These candidates are the best of the best, and we hired Valeria without hesitation on a 6 month contract.  Once her contract was up, I hired Valeria to work with us at DIRECTV full time.  \n\nValeria immediately impressed us with her professionalism, dedication and true creativity.  She is able to take on any task, and find ways to make them more efficient and more effective.  Although she was a recent graduate when we hired her, she was able to interact with vice presidents and directors from Fortune 500 companies without hesitation.  She also took on a multi-million dollar budget and was able to optimize the funds to grow DIRECTV Partnership Marketing to where it is today. \n\nI'm very proud to have had Valeria on my team, and I'd steal her in a minute if given the opportunity.  Any company would be hard pressed to find stronger millennial marketer.  You'll have to negotiate hard for her, but she's totally worth it.  ", "recommendations/0/name": "Valeria Navea", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Director of Growth Marketing at Pinterest 📌", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/valerianavea/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAZnVVcBbSOv9TLAzWlWhh87x8GPCUw5M90", "recommendations/1/context": "Leo was Kevin's client", "recommendations/1/date": "November 22, 2014", "recommendations/1/description": "I worked with Kevin for over 3 years while I was managing partnerships at DIRECTV.  Kevin is truly amazing-- He really strives to do the best job he can for his clients.  He was always there when I needed him- he made it a point to always be accessible to me.  Kevin is also a great relationship builder, and people like to work with him.  Through those relationships, he consistently came to the table with aggressive rates that he personally negotiated on behalf of me.  I appreciated all the work that Kevin did for me and the company- he made my life much easier.  ", "recommendations/1/name": "Kevin Vas", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Vice President at Media Resource Group", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kdvas/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAACfYy0B82RrliSkN2DzlybRd8gzy1p6SZQ", "recommendations/2/context": "Leo managed Scott directly", "recommendations/2/date": "April 11, 2013", "recommendations/2/description": "Marketing specialists are so ubiquitous these days, it is sometimes difficult to clear the clutter and find truly talented professionals that can deliver exceptional results.  Resumes say one thing, but I can truly attest, as Scott's manager for over 3 years, that he is one of the finest examples of this talent.  \n\nScott not only knows how to create strong marketing campaigns, but he also has the ability to analyze and report back on how to optimize these opportunities.  In addition to creating, executing and analyzing campaigns, his dynamic personality makes him genuinely a pleasure to work with.      \n\nWhile Scott is able to execute on a tactical basis, his career has led him to become a true visionary and strategic leader.  He is always trying to better himself, and is a prime example of someone who always strives to go \"from good to great.\"  Any company would be lucky to have him lead a multi-functional team.", "recommendations/2/name": "Scott Warriner", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Sr Product Director, Personalization & Intelligence at Realtor.com", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/scottwarriner/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAECjwoBT3NpM6UfeL3RiHctIaSmSvonmh8", "recommendations/3/context": "Leo worked with Kourosh but on different teams", "recommendations/3/date": "December 28, 2012", "recommendations/3/description": "Simply put,working with Kourosh makes your life easier.  His strong project managment skills and technical background makes those with a marketing background get their jobs done that much quicker.  Kourosh has been key to a flawless file transfer processes with one of DIRECTV's largest partners, reducing rejects to less than 1%.  He is always there when needed -- One of my favorite things about Kourosh is that he picks up the phone!  And if he doesn't immediately pick up, he always responds within 24 hours- something very key in a sales driven environment.  I can't say enough good things about Kourosh.  He'll be a true asset to any organization.", "recommendations/3/name": "Kourosh Khatiblou", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Digital Transformation & Technology Leader | Enterprise Modernization | GenAI | Cybersecurity | CIO Executive Partner", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kourosh-khatiblou-a8376923/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAATq7MMBjBRVjMPvs99ue9uyHC-GgfH5s7M", "recommendations/4/context": "Leo worked with Jennifer but they were at different companies", "recommendations/4/date": "December 28, 2012", "recommendations/4/description": "What a star!  Jennifer has done a fantastic job of managing the partnership between AAA Carolinas and DIRECTV.  In the last year, Jennifer has grown our business 28%, which in this climate is an extradorinary achievement.  She has been able to bring 'first to market' ideas to DIRECTV which has provided incremental revenue to both of our companies.  Her strong marketing background coupled with a wonderful personality makes Jennifer a real pleasure to work with.", "recommendations/4/name": "Jennifer H.", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "Marketing", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/jennifer-h-284ba83/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAC11YQBHPz_f0v-z0upotnaRPU2pvnGuD8", "recommendations/5/context": "Leo worked with Christine but they were at different companies", "recommendations/5/date": "April 5, 2011", "recommendations/5/description": "Christine is by far one of the strongest partnership marketing professionals that I had the pleasure of working with.  I worked with Christine as the drivers of the Best Western and AIR MILES partnership, having negotiated the contract, executing the launch and overseeing the marketing intiatives in a mutually benefical way.  \n\nChristine always came to the table with new and fresh ideas; and was able to sell them through her extensive history working with promotions, data and customer behavior in the loyalty space.  Not only professional, but Christine is amazing at relationship marketing- she's just plain fun to be around.    \n\nAIR MILES is extremely lucky to have such a strong player on its team.", "recommendations/5/name": "Christine Feren - Sabourin", "recommendations/5/subtitle": "Vice President, Marketing Services at Scotiabank", "recommendations/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/christine-feren-sabourin-a536902/", "recommendations/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAB0xt8BAnqGkEJ4TKEMZPAlNeeAr8CpLIY", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Yashasvi worked with Leo on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "February 7, 2021", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "Leo is a pleasure to work with. He lights up any room he enters and is exceptional at managing stakeholders. We've often pitched to clients collaboratively and Leo's support has expedited deals. His determination and positive attitude is contagious resulting in achieving targets effectively.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Yashasvi Nahata Zheng (Yashi, 雅莎)", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "VP, International Business @AmoyDx | Building AI-ML solutions | Ex- Amazon, Booking Holdings, Bayer", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/yashasvinahata/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAA3zmlQBEsfX_kx0S99U7vpSfmFI7S7AdiE", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Valeria reported directly to Leo", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "March 18, 2015", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "I had the privilege of having Leo as a boss and mentor during his time at DIRECTV. Leo is very passionate and has great vision for his work. Internally he built strong relationships allowing for very cool cross-functional programs to be developed. His success can be attributed to his proactive and results oriented nature. Leo is an excellent resource and a master at partnership marketing. He’s definitely an extremely valuable person to have on your team.", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Valeria Navea", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Director of Growth Marketing at Pinterest 📌", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/valerianavea/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAZnVVcBbSOv9TLAzWlWhh87x8GPCUw5M90", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Leo was Kevin's client", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "February 9, 2015", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Leo on a daily basis, while he was a Senior Manager with DIRECTV.  During that time, Leo constantly looked for new ways to grow and optimize the performance of the partnership marketing programs he managed.  Leo is very creative and thought outside the box to challenge the team to come up with new tactics that resonated with consumers.  Leo is results driven and his dedication to improving performance was recognized when many of the new tactics helped improve overall performance.  Leo is a true team player and I look forward to the opportunity of being able to work with him again.", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Kevin Vas", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Vice President at Media Resource Group", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kdvas/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAACfYy0B82RrliSkN2DzlybRd8gzy1p6SZQ", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Scott reported directly to Leo", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "May 24, 2011", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "Leo’s drive, attention to detail and leadership skills are second to none, and few indiviuals have had a larger and more positive impact on my career development. I very much consider Leo to be a mentor and I think he would be a tremendous asset to any orginization.", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Scott Warriner", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "Sr Product Director, Personalization & Intelligence at Realtor.com", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/scottwarriner/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAECjwoBT3NpM6UfeL3RiHctIaSmSvonmh8", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Anne J. worked with Leo on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "April 8, 2011", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Leo in a marketing capacity at Cold Stone Creamery.  It was his passion for the task-at-hand combined with his attention to detail that always amazed me.  At the same time, Leo has the keen ability to communicate and present forward thinking ideas that positioned him as a marketing leader amongst his peers.  This national ice cream chain was lucky to have Leo’s contribution to strategic alliances, regional sales efforts and national media planning/buying.", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Anne J. Christenson", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "Marketing Director, Doximity", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/annechristenson/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABdFuQBE5SJOIFzoh5CHNAysm2dtqIEqXU", "recommendationsReceived/5/context": "Lisa worked with Leo but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/5/date": "April 5, 2011", "recommendationsReceived/5/description": "Leo and I worked together for a period of about 5 years. MasterCard and Best Western were, and still are, strategic partners. Leo and I worked closely on a number of joint initiatives. I found him to be responsive, creative, organized and with a great grasp of what needs to be done to make a partnership successful. Not to mention his keen understanding of the hospitality space. It was always a pleasure to work with him!", "recommendationsReceived/5/name": "Lisa McCallum Basch", "recommendationsReceived/5/subtitle": "General Manager at Bread Financial", "recommendationsReceived/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/lmccallum/", "recommendationsReceived/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAAxwXkBMiJu3uBSSjQjauisGsJsVljnzNA", "recommendationsReceived/6/context": "Helen worked with Leo but on different teams", "recommendationsReceived/6/date": "March 25, 2011", "recommendationsReceived/6/description": "Having worked with Leo at Cold Stone Creamery, I experienced his talent first hand and learned from him often. Leo's creative and strategic approach to developing local store marketing programs and best practices consistently resulted in sales increases for franchisees. Leo is a dynamic public speaker whose message always excited the audience into action. His confident and positive personality resonates with business partners, co-workers, managers and executives. Wherever Leo goes, results are sure to follow.", "recommendationsReceived/6/name": "Helen Genualdi, PHR", "recommendationsReceived/6/subtitle": "Learning & Leadership Development Specialist at Dick's Sporting Goods", "recommendationsReceived/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/helen-genualdi-phr-39763b16/", "recommendationsReceived/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAANMJ2MBRbugi1rewQxAh3f3mZtQM5aKHTs", "recommendationsReceived/7/context": "Susan was Leo's client", "recommendationsReceived/7/date": "March 23, 2011", "recommendation